sp.p:
Then I'm afraid they'll quarrel at Play, and soon throw up the Cards;
Offering to pull her into the Closet.
Therefore my Dear Charming Angel, let us make a good use of our time.

Then mine as bravely double their Attacque;
[seizing her again]
And thus I wrest it from you. Nay struggle not; for all's in vain: Or Death or Victory; I am determin'd.
